ex04 >> now for this exercise you have to RTFM !! (Read the fuck**ng manual) using the <man> command 
        when using "man ls", search for the flags that do the following >> list all files and directories in your
        current directory (except for hidden files or any file that starts by a dot - yes, that
        includes double-dots), separated by a comma and a space, by order of modification
        date. Make sure the directoryâ€™s names are followed by a slash character.
